plot: Jeremy is worried about turning 40 and Mark is running out of time to win over April. How is it all going to end for the El Dude Brothers? Are they going to be alright?

Whilst Jeremy dreads approaching his fortieth birthday Mark gets fired after Jeremy reports him for granting him a loan he considers extortionate. A partially guilty Jeremy urges Mark to win back April, who is going on holiday with Angus and success seems likely until Mark discovers that Super Hans and Jeremy have kidnapped Angus and a surprise birthday party spells disaster for Hans, Mark and Jeremy.—don @ minifie-1
